data.description: Nestled in the heart of North Idaho, this 3 bed, 2 bath, 1560 sq ft home on a usable 5-acre property is a sanctuary of natural beauty, comfort, and community. Enjoy amazing views of Mt. Spokane ski area, abundant wildlife, diverse trees, and native plant life. The property is near Farragut State Park and a variety of fishing & boating lakes. The circular driveway has plenty of parking, and it provides easy access to the home & shop. The property features a 30 x 40 x 14 pole barn with a 12 x 40 partially closed in lean-to. It also has a heat pump and 50-amp generator hookup. A private well, shared with only five other homes, ensures a reliable and environmentally responsible water supply. The landscaping around the property has been meticulously maintained, adding to its natural beauty. The home also has an 18 x 28 cedar deck, a perfect spot for relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. This exceptional property offers the opportunity to own a slice of North Idaho's natural paradise!
